text": "in much demand, in traffic,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the market;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A 'Obeyd, S, K;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taAjirapN", "text_ar": "تَاجِرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (K:) or the latter, a she-camel"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is goodly, and saleable,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in much demand:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is easy of sale when offered, by reason of her excellence:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T:) or simply,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is easy of sale,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in much demand:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S:) as though, by reason of her beauty, or goodliness, and fatness, she sold herself: (Ksh in ii. 15:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "contr. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kaAsidapN", "text_ar": "كَاسِدَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (S, * TA:) the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tAjrp", "text_ar": "تاجرة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tawaAjiru", "text_ar": "تَوَاجِرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (T, A.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Ealayoka", "text_ar": "عَلَيْكَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biAls~ilaEi Alt~awaAjiri", "text_ar": "بِالسِّلَعِ التَّوَاجِرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Keep thou to the commodities"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that are saleable,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in much demand."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "huwa EalaY A^akorami taAjirapK", "text_ar": "هُوَ عَلَى اَكْرَمِ تَاجِرَةٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He is upon a most noble horse."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "K", "TA", "Msb", "A", "T"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}